<head>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-light p-4">
  <ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="myTab" role="tablist">
    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
      <button class="nav-link active" id="nav-tab-1" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#tab-1" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-1" aria-selected="true">Kiểm tra nhanh bằng cách thủ công</button>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
      <button class="nav-link" id="nav-tab-2" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#tab-2" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-2" aria-selected="false">Kiểm tra nhanh bằng cách upload file</button>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
      <button class="nav-link" id="nav-tab-3" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#tab-3" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-3" aria-selected="false">Gửi kết quả qua Email bằng cách nhập thủ công</button>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
      <button class="nav-link" id="nav-tab-4" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#tab-4" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-4" aria-selected="false">Gửi kết quả qua Email bằng cách upload file</button>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="tab-content" id="myTabContent">
    <div class="tab-pane fade show active bg-white" id="tab-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-tab-1">
      <form action="/search-by-input" method="POST" class="p-2">
        <p class="fs-4 text-danger">* Lưu ý: Chỉ sử dụng khi có ít hơn 10 domain và muốn xem kết quả nhanh chóng. Nếu có nhiều hơn, vui lòng sử dụng tính năng gửi kết quả qua Email!</p>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="domain" class="form-label">Domain:</label>
          <textarea class="form-control border border-secondary" id="domain" name="domain" rows="4" cols="50" placeholder="vtv.vn tuoitre.vn"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade bg-white" id="tab-2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-tab-2">
      <form action="/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="p-2">
        <p class="fs-4 text-danger">* Lưu ý: Chỉ sử dụng khi có ít hơn 10 domain và muốn xem kết quả nhanh chóng. Nếu có nhiều hơn, vui lòng sử dụng tính năng gửi kết quả qua Email!</p>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label class="form-label" for="file">File:</label>
          <input class="form-control border border-secondary" id="file" name="file" type="file">
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade bg-white" id="tab-3" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-tab-3">
      <form action="/search-by-input-email" method="POST" class="p-2">
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="email" class="form-label">Email:</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" type="email" class="form-control border border-secondary" required placeholder="abc@gmail.com">
          <label for="domain" class="form-label">Domain:</label>
          <textarea id="domain" name="domain" rows="4" cols="50" class="form-control border border-secondary" placeholder="vtv.vn tuoitre.vn"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade bg-white" id="tab-4" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-tab-4">
      <form action="/upload-email" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="p-2">
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="email" class="form-label">Email:</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" type="email" class="form-control border border-secondary" required placeholder="abc@gmail.com">
          <label for="file" class="form-label">File:</label>
          <input id="file" name="file" type="file" class="form-control border border-secondary">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-IQsoLXl5PILFhosVNubq5LC7Qb9DXgDA9i+tQ8Zj3iwWAwPtgFTxbJ8NT4GN1R8p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-cVKIPhGWiC2Al4u+LWgxfKTRIcfu0JTxR+EQDz/bgldoEyl4H0zUF0QKbrJ0EcQF" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>